channel.title: Teleporting problemi
channel.description: I changed the "ape atoll" teleport into "different teleports" which has 4 different teleporting options. However the only one that actually works is the first one. The rest of them just teleport me all to the same place. I'm fairly new to this still, so if someone could tell me what I'm doing wrong that would be great. Thanks.

item.title: Teleporting problemi
item.dc:creator: @1_2_3_4_KOED 1 2 3 4 KOED
item.description:
@1_2_3_4_KOED wrote:

Ah! A simple mistake for me. I had everything correct besides the teleAction. I thought you had to make the teleAction 1,2,3,4, but really they all should be 1. Thanks!

item.title: Teleporting problemi
item.dc:creator: @ohokay ohokay
item.description:
@ohokay wrote:

Each option for the teleport is a separate action button, which means it has a separate case.

For example, you’ll have

Teleport 1 - action button (500)
Teleport 2 - action button (501)
Teleport 3 - action button (502)
Teleport 4 - action button (503)

Note: These are not accurate action buttons.

You’ll have to add the teleport under the correct case.

Read full topic
